snippet.title: God of Light: Azure Tree (World 3) Walkthrough Solution, Source of Life 19-20
snippet.description:
This is a video walkthrough for the iOS and Android game by Playmous, God of Light Azure Tree, levels 19 & 20. See the rest of my walkthrough here, including all firefly locations: http://www.appunwrapper.com/2014/02/27/god-of-light-walkthrough-and-strategy-guide/ Let me know if you need a video of any other levels.

See all my God of Light videos here: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuhgk1TKevasrx05je6y-vSPnRg48pmJd
